<div id="community-vibe">
    <h2 class="sect-title">Community Vibe in Bel-Aire</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">Bel-Aire ticks all the right boxes on the real estate checklist.With abundant greenery in
                the vicinity in the form of parklands and the Calgary Golf Club, Bel-Aire offers scenic views of the
                Rocky Mountains, winding pathways, and the Glenmore Reservoir.</p>
            <p class="par-xl">Extra peace and quiet in a luxurious setting, is what sets Bel-Aire real estate apart.
            </p>

            <p class="par-lg">Chinook Centre is Calgary’s largest indoor shopping centre and is located East of
                Bel-Aire. Housing over 250 stores, plus a Scotiabank Theatre complex, the mall has a variety of
                different boutiques for all peoples interests, whether it be fashion styles or other.</p>

            <p class="par-lg">Making up the Northern portion of the community is the Calgary Golf & Country Club,
                Alberta’s oldest 18-hole golf course. Bel-Aire is a short drive away from scenic hiking trails in North
                Glenmore Park and Weaselhead, which are perfect areas for day hikes, picnics, bonfires, and barbeques.
                Weaselhead also proves to have a wonderful view of the sun setting sky, one of Alberta’s true natural
                beauties</p>

        </div>
